reviewText: Very enjoyable and amusing:hope there are more.
This serie is amazing, I saw it before and my kids will love to have it in DVD.

These discs can be played in the US with a blu ray player.  These videos are so cute.  I had to download the Season 1 videos from You Tube.  Took some time to find ones that had the recording quality to warrant the download.  But, with these discs, that was not necessary for Season 2.  Yea!
